</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 6:15:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> Hello fellahs !<br><br>You know what ?! I trashed my Epic and failed today.<br>Not a common news on the TSH boards :)<br><br>The trouble went when I tried to spawn the General.<br>Here is what I do, steps by steps.<br><br>(Environnement : DE cabin cleaned, 8am, no wanderers, all clean except the Brigadier)<br><br>1) I'm Hidden/Sneaking behind the Brigadier (no problem)<br>2) I'hand the sealed box (no problem)<br>3) Trade dialog box open (no problem)<br>4) I click on trade button (AGGRO)<br>5) Death<br><br>Brigadier aggroed as soon as I clicked.<br>He ripped me.<br>He took the box.<br>The General didn't spawn.<br><br>My assassin friend had the same problem trying just after me.<br><br>So ?<br>Where is the trouble ? What is wrong ?<br><br>Surely, we both petitioned.<br>And a GM went (Blixtev IIRC), calling us "lad", explaining we are dumb and did the quest in the bad way. We both are wrong to him. So he didn't gave back any sealed box nor didn't checked the brigadier.<br><br>Now I have my Epic to do again and my friend assassin we'll soon be on DAoC I guess.<br><br>Guys, I need you to tell me your steps to give the box. I thought those where the good ones and I just can't imagine what else to do.<br><br>Thanx for helping.<br><br>Odastre PerceFlanc.<br>Just another rogue. Server Karana. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unwardezir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>nwardezir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0> at: 4/7/02 6:17:32 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unark84.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nark84</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 7:59:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> Sorry to hear about this. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>First, get up behind the one inkie you leave in the cabin (Brigadier for you I guess), only using Sneak, no Hide. With Sneak still on, put 1 copper in the trade window, and proceed to click Trade. If you don't get agro, do the same thing with your box instead of the copper (JUST Sneak, NO Hide). If you DID get agro with the copper, just die and turn in coppers 'til you don't get agro. Good luck!<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Nark<br>52 Halfling Rogue<br>&lt;The Far Eastwood&gt;<br>Ayonae Ro</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharafi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharafi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 7:59:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> You have to drop hide before you give him the box.<br><br>Here is a tip... Drop hide ( Not sneak ), hand a coin to the inkie and trade it... wait a few seconds, if you get agro you only lose a coin, if no agro its safe to hand in ya box..<br><br>As soon as you hand in the box, hit hide before the General spawns..<br><br>Cake<br><br>EDIT: Gah i type too slow :P <br><br>Sharafi Lim'Dul 58 Templar &lt;Red Sky&gt;<br>Farkuu Soultaker 54 Reaver<br>Zebarti Lim'Dul 54 Rake &lt;Red Sky&gt;<br>Others Still In The Shadows.<br>Bertoxx <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usharafi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sharafi</A> at: 4/7/02 8:00:37 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umongomfh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mongo mfh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 8:37:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> Is also nice to have the mob hit with a harmony before attempting the turn-in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukalatheknevrseen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalathek Nevrseen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 9:36:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> I had hide up when I turned my stuff in...put up a copper, no agro put up the box, wait 5 seconds, hand in...worked fine for me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulannellavelglarn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lannella Velglarn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/lannella/leaf.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/7/02 9:37:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> We had this exact thing happen to one of our rogues the other night (when I did mine 2nd, after him).<br><br>Answers already given.  <br>*  Use a coin test.  <br>*  Drop Hide manually first.  <br>*  Don't go through the window but get 100% behind him in the cabin.<br><br><br>Good luck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upyrocatmoonstalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pyrocat Moonstalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/8/02 1:02:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4652.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Details of steps for the secret handoff on Epic.</span><hr size=1> OMFG!!<br><br>"And a GM went (Blixtev IIRC), calling us "lad", explaining we are dumb and did the quest in the bad way. We both are wrong to him. So he didn't gave back any sealed box nor didn't checked the brigadier"<br><br>EXACT same thing happened to me (I'm on prexus also) except he called me lass instead of lad (and I'm a guy).<br><br>Had to restart epic, which I have now /bonk <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.